picked_headlines.summary: Kandinsky 5.0 introduces advanced models for high-res image and video generation, emphasizing innovative training techniques and open-source accessibility.
picked_headlines.reason_for_choice: Kandinsky 5.0 is a significant advancement in image and video generation, appealing to both technical audiences interested in model architecture and stakeholders interested in product development and open-source contributions.

picked_headlines.summary: A Two-Pass Adaptive Inference algorithm optimizes YOLOv10s on consumer GPUs, enhancing performance without architectural changes.
picked_headlines.reason_for_choice: This paper offers practical insights into improving AI performance on consumer hardware, making it relevant for engineers and product managers seeking cost-effective solutions.

digest:
- *OpenBioLLM* enhances genomic Q&A with modular multi-agent systems, outperforming GeneGPT in efficiency and accuracy. Read more: https://arxiv.org/abs/2511.15061
- *Nemotron Elastic* offers a cost-effective framework for multi-scale LLMs, achieving significant training efficiency. Explore: https://arxiv.org/abs/2511.16664
- *Prism* decouples ranking and explanation in recommendation systems, enhancing personalization. Details: https://arxiv.org/abs/2511.16543
- *MAIF* proposes an artifact-centric AI paradigm for enhancing trust and regulatory compliance. More info: https://arxiv.org/abs/2511.15097
- *MergeDNA* introduces dynamic tokenization for genomic modeling, improving DNA task performance. Check it out: https://arxiv.org/abs/2511.14806
- *AgentSwift* improves LLM agent design via hierarchical search, enhancing performance. Discover: https://arxiv.org/abs/2506.06017
- *MOON* addresses multimodal challenges in e-commerce product understanding with innovative techniques. Learn more: https://arxiv.org/abs/2508.11999
- *DriveReg* offers a framework for autonomous vehicles to interpret traffic laws using AI, enhancing safety. Read: https://arxiv.org/abs/2410.04759
- *FLARE* enhances federated learning's resilience against malicious clients with adaptive reputation scoring. Find out more: https://arxiv.org/abs/2511.14715
- *DeepThinkVLA* integrates reasoning and action in VLA models, achieving state-of-the-art results. Explore: https://arxiv.org/abs/2511.15669
